\c 12
\p
\v 1 Imwi Jehovha, makarurama, pandinokakavadzana nemwi, zvakadaro ndichataura nemwi \add zve\add*mitongo \add yenyu.\add* Sei nzira dzevakaipa dzichibudirira, \add uye \add*vagere zvakanaka vese vanonyengera nekunyengera?
\v 2 Imwi makavasima, zvirokwazvo vakadzika midzi; vanokura, zvirokwazvo vanobereka zvibereko; imwi muri pedo nemiromo yavo, asi muri kure nemoyo yavo.
\v 3 Asi imwi Jehovha munondiziva; makandiona, uye makaidza moyo wangu kwamuri, vadzurei semakwai ekubaiwa, uye muagadzirire zuva rekubaiwa.
\v 4 Nyika ichachema kusvika rinhi, nemiriwo yesango rese ichasvava? Nekuda kwekuipa kwevagari vayo, mhuka neshiri zvinoparara, nokuti vanoti haangaoni mugumo wedu.
\p
\v 5 Kana wakamhanya nevetsoka, vakakunetesa, zvino ungakwikwidzana nemabhiza sei? Kana uchivimba nenyika yerunyararo, uchaita sei pakukukumara kweJoridhani?
\v 6 Nokuti kunyange hama dzako neimba yababa vako, naivo vakaita nekunyengera pamwe newe, hongu, ivo vakadanidzira shure kwako zvakazara, usavavimba, kunyange vakataura mashoko akanaka kwauri.
\s Jehovha achatonga Judha nevavengi vavo
\p
\v 7 Ndasiya imba yangu, ndarasa nhaka yangu; ndapa mudikanwi wemoyo wangu muruoko rwemuvengi wake.
\v 8 Nhaka yangu yava kwandiri seshumba iri mudondo; yandibudisira inzwi; naizvozvo ndakaivenga.
\v 9 Nhaka yangu kwandiri igondo rine mavara here? Magora akaikomba kuirwisa. Uyai muunganidze zvikara zvese zvesango, muzviunze kuti zvidye.
\v 10 Vafudzi vazhinji vakaparadza munda wangu wemizambiringa, vakatsika-tsika mugove wangu pasi petsoka dzavo, vakaita mugove wangu unofadza uve renje riri dongo.
\v 11 Vakauita dongo; unochemera kwandiri uri dongo, nyika yese yakaitwa dongo, nokuti hakuna munhu ano\add u\add*isa pamoyo.
\v 12 Vaparadzi vakasvika pamidunduru yese murenje; nokuti munondo waJehovha uchapedza kubva kumugumo wenyika kusvika kumugumo wenyika; hakuna nyama ichava nerugare.
\v 13 Vakadzvara gorosi, asi vachakohwa minzwa; vakazvitambudza, asi havangavi nepundutso; uye muchanyara negoho renyu, nekuda kwekutsamwa kunopfuta kwaJehovha.
\p
\v 14 Anoreva seizvi Jehovha: Pamusoro pevekwangu vese vakaipa vanobata nhaka yandakagarisa vanhu vangu Israeri: Tarira, ndichavadzura panyika yavo, uye ndichadzura imba yaJudha kubva pakati pavo.
\v 15 Zvino zvichaitika shure kwekunge ndavadzura, ndichadzoka, uye ndichavanzwira tsitsi, ndigovadzosera umwe neumwe kunhaka yake, uye umwe neumwe kunyika yekwake.
\v 16 Zvino zvichaitika, kana vakashingairira kudzidza nzira dzevanhu vangu, kupika nezita rangu, neUpenyu hwaJehovha, sezvavakadzidzisa vanhu vangu kupika nabhaari, ipapo vachavakwa pakati pevanhu vangu.
\v 17 Asi kana vasingateereri, ndichadzura kwazvo nekuparadza rudzi irwo, anoreva Jehovha.